Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.30,0:02:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"The Pact Between Men!\NThe Fierce Fighting of Brachio Tank!"{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.81,0:02:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Big Mom?! Why is she here?!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.07,0:02:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh, no! Oh, no! She'll eat me!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.07,0:02:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh, no! Oh, no...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.58,0:02:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Tank Commander Chopper!\NTank Commander Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.37,0:02:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Since we're disguising ourselves\Nas the Animal Kingdom Pirates crew,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.63,0:02:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure she thinks we're her allies!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.92,0:02:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.13,0:02:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.34,0:03:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I forgot we were disguising ourselves\Nas the enemy!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.26,0:03:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.72,0:03:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a report!\NThis is Tank Commander Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.35,0:03:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He just introduced himself as Chopper!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.40,0:03:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm on security detail for the banquet!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.99,0:03:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're on patrol.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.16,0:03:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She believed him!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.63,0:03:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That was close!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.59,0:03:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,He looks awfully familiar...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.14,0:03:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's him!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.06,0:03:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.14,0:03:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the raccoon from Straw Hat's group!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.81,0:03:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Driver Usopp!\NRetreat at full speed! Retreat at full speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.36,0:03:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.99,0:04:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.53,0:04:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it wouldn't work!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.33,0:04:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.91,0:04:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Raccoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.16,0:04:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Retreat at full speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.84,0:04:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,They're gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.21,0:04:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,--Chobro!\N--That's one fierce mature woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.80,0:04:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.81,0:04:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,On the way here, he cut the rope and tried to escape\Nso I knocked him out!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.49,0:04:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not worry. He is alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.58,0:04:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,How could you do that to\Nthe heir of Kozuki who was once your lord...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.75,0:04:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so cold and heartless!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.46,0:05:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I've finished playing the role\Nso now he is just a brat I do not know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.05,0:05:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm surprised! I indeed remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.14,0:05:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You're one of the Akazaya Nine\Nthat I faced off against 20 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.65,0:05:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes... I remember you well, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.73,0:05:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I was disappointed to know you were the son of\Nthat brave Oden 20 years ago and you haven't changed a bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.53,0:05:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, he is just a shitty brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.25,0:05:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,He just happens to have such a great lineage...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.59,0:05:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, poor boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.01,0:05:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,How could you punch such a little boy\Nuntil he bleeds.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.98,0:06:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, drink! Let's make a toast first!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.98,0:06:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You've done well\Nserving as a spy for so long!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.19,0:06:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Good job!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.95,0:06:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,No, Orochi-{\i1}sama{\i}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.99,0:06:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I failed to intercept the Akazaya's plan...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.66,0:06:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,...due to the Straw Hats and other pirate groups'\Nsurprise attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.62,0:06:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! Failed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.59,0:06:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The rebel forces, 5,400 strong,\Nare advancing towards Onigashima now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.01,0:06:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Luffy?!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.47,0:06:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Are they still alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.22,0:06:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,S-So are you saying that\Nth-the Akazaya members are still around?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.15,0:06:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Screw you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.31,0:06:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You failed to intercept their plan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.44,0:06:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I am deeply sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.03,0:06:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one who told me\Nthat they'd rendezvous at Tokage Port!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.66,0:06:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you exterminate them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.79,0:06:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,K-Kin'emon outsmarted me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.25,0:07:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew him for a long time,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.96,0:07:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,but I did not know he was that tactical!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.13,0:07:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't make excuses!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.59,0:07:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me, Kanjuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.88,0:07:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Will the samurai's fleet come to Onigashima?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.06,0:07:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems like it's still safe here, Orochi-{\i1}sama{\i}.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.64,0:07:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Fukurokuju!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.39,0:07:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,There are no suspicious ships at the port.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.23,0:07:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,However, three of our warships\Nhaven't returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.07,0:07:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.74,0:07:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,...saw two of those ships\Nbeing sunk by the damn pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.25,0:07:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, it's reasonable to assume that\Nthe other ship was sunk as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.51,0:07:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, on the Performance Floor out there,\Nwe confirmed four pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.93,0:08:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Straw Hat Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.81,0:08:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Pirate Hunter Zoro.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.32,0:08:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Eustass "Captain" Kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.24,0:08:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,"Murder Machine" Killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.74,0:08:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The members from both of their pirate groups\Nhave very likely entered the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.00,0:08:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,If you knew that, why didn't you report it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.00,0:08:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Queen-{\i1}dono{\i} was handling it,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.00,0:08:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,so I thought I'd better not spoil the banquet...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.46,0:08:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether they're here of not,\Nall our forces are here on Onigashima.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.30,0:08:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever happens,\Nthis is the safest place in the country!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.44,0:08:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.48,0:08:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Drink, Orochi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.36,0:08:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Here! Have a cup.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.57,0:08:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm... mm-hm...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.16,0:09:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No... I don't want any consolation!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.95,0:09:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'd rather hear a report\Nthat the damn samurai have been killed!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.84,0:09:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sure it's gonna be fine!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.46,0:09:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Everyone must be here on Onigashima!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.13,0:09:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Because Luffy's here!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.68,0:09:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Survive however you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.81,0:09:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna come rescue you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.44,0:09:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have to get away!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.48,0:09:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I must survive...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.57,0:09:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...however I can!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.03,0:09:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Black Maria!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.53,0:09:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Give him to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.53,0:09:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! We must not forget!\NHe's the leader of the enemies!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.87,0:09:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Set the execution stage!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.04,0:09:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,If their iconic Kozuki Family dies out,\Ntheir mouldering loyalty will crumble away, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.59,0:09:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And it'll all be over!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.64,0:10:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Luffy...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.89,0:10:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Everyone...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.31,0:10:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Father...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.94,0:10:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Are they all okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.49,0:10:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, of course they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.08,0:10:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Izo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.24,0:10:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for everything, Cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.45,0:10:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,He said everyone's already entered the island\Nso I guess the raid is underway!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.38,0:10:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That lonely island is now called Onigashima, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.92,0:10:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiku...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.88,0:10:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, you left before me\Nbut you're arriving at the same time as me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.26,0:10:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't need to entrust you\Nwith my message to Straw Hat Luffy-{\i1}yoi{\i}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.39,0:10:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right! I'll throw this note out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.32,0:10:57.74,On Top,,0,0,0,,I'LL BE LATE BUT I'LL BE THERE - MARCO
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.65,0:11:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,--You said you're gonna go to the Land of Wano?\N--Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.53,0:11:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you planning to do there?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.12,0:11:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll take down Kaido!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.79,0:11:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll do it! We'll avenge Oden-{\i1}sama{\i}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.29,0:11:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The Straw Hats will help us!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.21,0:11:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.72,0:11:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I have even more reason to come with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.68,0:11:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I can't believe you came, Marco.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.31,0:11:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, because I always liked Oden...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.52,0:11:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my friend's home which he risked his life to save.\NHow can I not help?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.98,0:11:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you. I'm indebted to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.24,0:11:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say that.\NI should've done something sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.36,0:11:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe how much Oden's country\Nhas changed...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.16,0:11:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Information about the Land of Wano\Ndoesn't cross the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.87,0:11:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know the once rich Land of Wano\Nwas in such a state...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.75,0:11:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all because of Kaido.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.38,0:12:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you're now determined!\NLet's hurry to Onigashima!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.09,0:12:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We must catch up to everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.68,0:12:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But what should we do?\NTheir raid has already started.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.27,0:12:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,How do we join them\Nin the presence of the enemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.02,0:12:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Count on me! I have an idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.78,0:12:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As planned, Denjiro is leading the Southern Forces\Ntoward the back entrance of the castle.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.69,0:12:25.70,On Top,,0,0,0,,SOUTHERN FORCES - DENJIRO'S GROUP
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.78,0:12:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,There's an undocumented gate!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.95,0:12:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,They must've extended the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.25,0:12:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hide!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.46,0:12:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it a top officer? What a pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.84,0:12:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,--Listen! Find him as quickly as possible!\N--Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.26,0:12:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not so much of a pain after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.97,0:12:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I know him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.93,0:12:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go talk to him...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.06,0:12:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.22,0:12:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, it's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.93,0:12:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.14,0:12:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.27,0:12:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.27,0:12:58.94,On Top,,0,0,0,,SASAKI, TOBI ROPPO, ANIMAL KINGDOM PIRATES
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.56,0:13:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Kyoshiro! I heard you weren't coming this year!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.36,0:13:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, don't tell anyone about me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.49,0:13:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You're here incognito?\NWhat happened to your special faux-pompadour?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.20,0:13:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's unusual for you to leave a banquet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.16,0:13:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Kaido-{\i1}san{\i}'s kid went missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.62,0:13:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,--Anyway, would you like to drink?\N--Yes, I would!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.25,0:13:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Guys, go back to the Skull Dome!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.04,0:13:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll join you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.92,0:13:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The gate that wasn't on the blueprints.\NAnd one of the Tobi Roppo, Sasaki.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.14,0:13:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}However, for Kyoshiro\Nwho was trusted by the enemy for so long,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.77,0:13:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}they were easy obstacles to overcome.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.82,0:13:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Sea Prism Stone?!\NHey, what are you doing, Kyoshiro?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.61,0:13:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,--Tie him up!\N--Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.91,0:13:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.74,0:13:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,--Cover his mouth, too!\N--Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.49,0:13:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Answer me, Kyoshiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.75,0:13:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Sasaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.67,0:14:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know the Land of Wano's history?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.88,0:14:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.51,0:14:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}After restraining one of the formidable Tobi Roppo,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.72,0:14:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Denjiro split his group into two\Njust as the Eastern Forces did.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.31,0:14:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,--Get inside the dome from here!\N--Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.48,0:14:25.07,On Top,,0,0,0,,DOME INFILTRATION TEAM
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.07,0:14:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thus, the Southern Forces are steadily closing in on Kaido!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.53,0:14:28.86,On Top,,0,0,0,,RAID TEAM
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.26,0:14:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,How annoying those fools are!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.64,0:14:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did you go, raccoon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.68,0:15:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got to pay for the wedding cake!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.31,0:15:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Majesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.65,0:15:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We heard you want to destroy a tank\Nso we came in haste!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.65,0:15:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. Then why don't you take up\Nyour positions already to smoke them out?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.70,0:15:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.58,0:15:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Tank Commander Chopper, what should we do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.00,0:15:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't look good!\NThey're each setting up traps with the intent to shoot us!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.42,0:15:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.84,0:15:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We're finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.88,0:15:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Tank Commander Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.21,0:15:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you remember our purpose?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.84,0:15:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Our purpose?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.09,0:15:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Our mission is to rejoin Franky and the Black Rhino\Nat the promised hill,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.56,0:15:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and combine to become the General Franky!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.77,0:15:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.02,0:15:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That combo is our best shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.94,0:15:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Your animal instincts are\Nthe only hope we have to get through this situation!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.03,0:15:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Driver Usopp...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.20,0:15:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right. I guess I got too frazzled.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.96,0:16:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,If we can't trust this Brachio Tank,\Nwho else will?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.34,0:16:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Tank Commander Chopper, your order sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.63,0:16:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go! Charge at full speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.01,0:16:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.18,0:16:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The enemy's lying in ambush at the slit in the wall!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.60,0:16:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,When I give the cue,\Nturn round by drifting!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.36,0:16:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.82,0:16:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, Brachio!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.90,0:16:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.57,0:16:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, fire back!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.25,0:16:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Launch mortar attacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.38,0:16:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.52,0:17:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,There are massive cannons ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.02,0:17:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Charge, don't hesitate!\NWe'll get them at close range!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.66,0:17:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Now! Driver Usopp, show them what you've got!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.58,0:17:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.38,0:17:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,They took them all down... Not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.97,0:17:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But now I know where the raccoon is!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.81,0:17:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know the weak point of a tank?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.23,0:17:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an attack from right above!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.44,0:17:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Mom Bomber strikes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.24,0:17:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,She's above us! Let's get away at full speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.37,0:18:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop the tank!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.83,0:18:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, Commander?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.71,0:18:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Trust the thickness of Brachio Tank's armor!\NThere must be a way out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.59,0:18:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's rest our fate on Brachio Tank.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.60,0:18:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.07,0:18:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Go to hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.41,0:18:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Driver Usopp, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.37,0:18:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! A point-blank shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.25,0:18:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's some extra candy! Enjoy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.35,0:19:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,We won, didn't we, Driver Usopp?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.48,0:19:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Tank Commander, it's a total victory!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.19,0:19:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Expertly commanded, Tank Commander Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.86,0:19:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,No, we survived thanks to your shooting skills!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.24,0:19:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, it was a tough battle...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.74,0:19:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Commander, let's meet up with everyone else!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.58,0:19:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. Let's go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.33,0:19:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys, you don't really think\Nyou can bring me down that easily,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.80,0:19:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,do you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.68,0:19:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Screw you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.85,0:19:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Commander, w-what is your order...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.64,0:19:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You know what I would say...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.19,0:19:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Make a strategic retreat!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.77,0:19:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it wouldn't work out!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.57,0:20:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.19,0:20:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Raccoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.66,0:20:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though they were frightened,\Nthey ran in the opposite direction...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.75,0:20:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Commander Chopper, Driver Usopp...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.08,0:20:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's move on!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.92,0:20:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.13,0:20:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone! Don't let the sacrifice go to waste!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.09,0:20:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, shouldn't we do something?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.05,0:20:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that monstrous mature woman\Nis too much for those two boys to handle!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.31,0:20:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,She's right! It's Big Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.60,0:20:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's why there's nothing we can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.06,0:20:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's just thank them for luring her away!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.27,0:20:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, why is it so hot here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.53,0:20:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Nami! Look up! We're in trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.53,0:20:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I found you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.03,0:20:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the woman who kidnapped Zeus, Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.50,0:20:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.96,0:21:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryuo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.76,0:21:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.23,0:21:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.36,0:21:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Pay-Pay! Pay-Pay! Pay-Pay!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.28,0:21:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Go for it! Pay-Pay!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.45,0:21:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Go for it! Pay-Pay!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.95,0:21:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Go look elsewhere, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.75,0:21:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What, Pay-Pay?! Did you call me an idiot?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.08,0:21:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! You're an idiot!\NIdiot, idiot, idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.42,0:21:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Say that I'm a wonderful Big Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.09,0:21:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.18,0:21:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't run anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.80,0:21:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Pay-Pay! I'm tired-{\i1}arinsu{\i}!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.06,0:21:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.27,0:22:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no energy left...\NEven my dear brother is taking me for a fool...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.90,0:22:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Poor me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.65,0:22:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't bother me!\NIf you're tired, just sit there!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.36,0:22:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Why can't you say...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.28,0:22:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.37,0:22:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,..."Let me carry you on my back"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.50,0:22:20.50,On Top,,0,0,0,,ULTI AND PAGE ONE\NTOBI ROPPO, ANIMAL KINGDOM PIRATES
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.87,0:22:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, get off of me! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.67,0:22:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Let go of me! Big Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.46,0:22:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You little...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.46,0:22:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Stop it! I mean it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.26,0:22:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Pay-Pay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.01,0:22:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Pay-Pay! Pay-Pay! Pay-Pay!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.81,0:22:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay, stay, stay with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.94,0:22:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my Pay-Pay!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.65,0:22:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What the?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.36,0:22:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Pay-Pay!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.95,0:22:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Pay-Pay sacrificed himself to save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.12,0:23:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Who the hell are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.17,0:23:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are {\i1}you{\i}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.31,0:23:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Acknowledged as a strong enemy!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.14,0:23:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Color of the Supreme King, used by the man who aspires\Nto be King of the Pirates, surprises Ulti and Page One.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.19,0:23:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When they are about to attack Luffy in their beast forms,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.65,0:23:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}a stranger in a demon mask appears\Nwith the sound of wooden clogs.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.62,0:23:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,On the next episode of One Piece!\N"Thunder Bagua! Here Comes Kaido's Son!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.12,0:23:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
